  <h1>How to Play OfficeWars</h1>
  <p>In OfficeWars your are in a rat race to become the most powerful office supply trader in the world! The goal of the game is to comfortably retire with your massive stockpiles of office supplies... unfortunately, office snitches are trying to stand in your way and it is your job to destroy them!</p>
  <p>OfficeWars offers 2 different play dynamics. You can become a big shot off trading alone, or you can battle your way through the bosses to acquire elite loot and make the really big sales.</p>
  
